1. LinkRiseUp Audit As Template Candidate

LinkRiseUp ab ek normal site nahi, ek base product candidate hai.
Isko template banane ke liye hume code ko 3 buckets me dekhna hoga:

A. Core reusable logic
Ye har site me same rehna chahiye:

master panel connector
feed fetching
task rendering system
post detail pages
search framework
sitemap/robots
metadata framework
schema helpers
indexing hooks
comments system
pagination
reusable cards
deploy/docker/nginx/github-actions setup
B. Site-config driven parts
Ye per site change hona chahiye:

site name
domain
site code
logo
contact info
social links
enabled tasks
default categories
SEO defaults
homepage section copy
header/footer labels
C. Theme/UI driven parts
Ye visually change honi chahiye:

colors
typography
spacing
hero layout
card style
icon style
section shapes/backgrounds
homepage composition
Audit result
LinkRiseUp template candidate tab banega jab:

hardcoded site references remove ho
config-first naming ho
common logic isolated ho
theme layer alag ho
panel integration stable ho
So yes: LinkRiseUp is a strong base, but abhi ise template-grade cleanup chahiye.

