5. Master Panel Role Define Clearly

Ye part bahut important hai.
Panel ko over-control nahi dena.

Master Panel should control
site registry
site status
API keys
task enablement
publishing flow
feed monitoring
indexing monitoring
sitemap live status
SEO audit
page-level SEO overrides
domain/runtime status
content performance analytics
Master Panel should NOT control
raw page layout
component-level styling
hero design
card animation design
page-specific visual composition
Why:

UI freedom chahiye
every site visually different ho sakti hai
panel ko operations center rehna hai, page builder nahi
Best definition
Master Site Panel = operations + publishing + SEO + indexing + monitoring control center

Not:
Master Site Panel = full visual website builder

